title: Celebrity Gossip Part 2 - Drake Jokes About Someone Getting Shot
description: Drake dropped a new album with 21 Savage and he decided to rap about Megan Thee Stallion, but not in a good way. And Britney Spears isn’t calling anyone out today, she’s actually issuing an apology for something she did 15 years ago.
